list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Feat: Implement Room database for Result feature
This commit introduces the local database setup for the `feature:result` module using Room Persistence Library.
**Key Changes:**
- **`ResultDatabase.kt`**: - Created an abstract `ResultDatabase` class extending `RoomDatabase`. - Defined `CourseEntity` and `ResultListEntity` as entities for the database. - Set `exportSchema = true` and `version = 11`. - Registered `DateConverter` for handling `Date` type conversion. - Declared an abstract `resultDao()` method. - Defined `DB_NAME` constant as "result\_db". - **`DateConverter.kt`**: - Added a new `DateConverter` class with `@TypeConverter` methods: - `fromTimestamp(Long?): Date?` to convert Long to Date. - `toTimestamp(Date?): Long?` to convert Date to Long.
**IDE Configuration Files:** The following Android Studio IDE configuration files were added: - `.idea/AndroidProjectSystem.xml` - `.idea/deviceManager.xml` - `.idea/vcs.xml` - `.idea/caches/deviceStreaming.xml` (contains a list of device configurations)
**Local Properties:** - `local.properties` file was created, primarily to define `sdk.dir`.
